column2: Do not try to invade the Valyrian Freehold…
Do not provoke the Bronze King…
Braavos is the weakest republic in the game," but has the potential to bceome the strongest.
The Arbor/Oldtown feud will be bloody…
Do not allow the Ironborn to unite…
Do not invade Dorne by land…
As Riverrun it is best to swear fealty to someone," or you may soon be destroyed.
Prince Tristifer 'The Hammer of Justice' Mudd
As the Viceroy to the Valyrian Freehold," beware revolts...
Do not let the moral authority of the Seven fall…
The Seven Kingdoms can be formed only through fear and blood…
